  <name>Diction</name>
  <summary>A high-performance, multi-format offline dictionary</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Look up words across all your installed dictionaries simultaneously and compare results in a clean interface.</p>
    <p>It lets you search across multiple dictionary sources at once, with a tabbed layout that makes comparing definitions simple and efficient.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Simultaneous search across multiple dictionaries</li>
      <li>Support for StarDict, MDict, and other formats</li>
      <li>Clean, responsive GTK4 interface</li>
      <li>Works fully offline</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
